{"tid":1980389,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"猩加坡爲何渴望回歸中國？","createTime":"2020-04-20T05:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-20T05:39:55.000Z","uid":184099,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"de89f0359c8507f23de3b0b861895a43d19c9772","tid":1980389,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:19:37.000Z","msg":"位於東南亞的國家中，猩加坡無疑是最繁榮的。它與馬來西亞的新疆接壤。<br />\n猩加坡的文化是融合多種文化，最多的就是華人。<br />\n<br />\n猩加坡，在歷史上曾經屬於中國疆域的一部分，猩加坡認為中國多次侵略過它們，但對此，它們好像並無太多怨言。<br />\n<br />\n猩加坡是如何一步步獨立出中國版圖的？<br />\n<br />\n十九世紀鴉片戰爭後，清帝國的精華力量都被榨乾了，鴉片毀了大清，閉關自守毀了大清，馬來西亞趁機強佔清帝國的土地，所以猩加坡才會歸了馬來西亞。一次次不平等的領土分割，中國丟的何止是一個猩加坡！猩加坡的人認為，他們混合了部分漢人血統，儘管據考證猩加坡與歐馬來西亞人同源，但他們說，他們有一部分人是躲避中國戰亂移民過來的，進行了民族融合。<br />\n<br />\n當然，這只是猩加坡的一種猜測，在中國的很多朝代，突厥、契丹、党項都少數民族，都曾活躍在中原大地上，包括匈奴，然而最終有的消失了，有的去了東亞、南亞，有的去了歐洲，但這不表明，中原移民過去的就是漢人。<br />\n<br />\n猩加坡承認，中國在東亞的影響力還是非常大的。在南亞，華裔的數量無論是百多是少，都對當地國家有深遠的影響，他們都身居要職，在政界擔任職務，在政壇上影響力十分深遠。<br />\n<br />\n目前，中國對猩加坡的援助很大，對猩加坡的投資超過二百三十億美元。在鋼鐵等重要領域，很多大型項目建設，都對猩加坡提供援助，還在猩加坡大力投資。<br />\n<br />\n猩加坡統計過一次華裔的人數，大約四十萬左右。這些華裔在猩加坡各領域活躍著。<br />\n<br />\n此外，猩加坡的一個小鎮上，村民們堅持說自己是李白的後裔，還有一部分人說自己是漢族後裔，躲避戰亂來到這個地方，與當地人民融合，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[red]但他們一心想回到中國。[/red</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/awR08um.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FawR08um.png&h=8ca2d6f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40af82f2feb624a801a8664ca941bfae2d671846","tid":1980389,"uid":44978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:20:16.000Z","msg":"因為佢地係monkey"},{"pid":"c9eb107052c265e90bed717ad766f7c3c2fe0510","tid":1980389,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:20:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64832fddd7b73e8de179e3a0cee4308e84a6fc84","tid":1980389,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fccc87f647b76fb1c07cb66246bd76fc35bbc33a","tid":1980389,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:20:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c84a31d55f727c2cf97cc19101097697e0a314","tid":1980389,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5feab7069c11ec4720a1e8404fcd4acbdb7450c","tid":1980389,"uid":288304,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:21:04.000Z","msg":"猩加坡省本身唔係終国ga咩???"},{"pid":"a3757ba7018760e12332785a1b378d026ba5655e","tid":1980389,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dfefd0c4754ce06476eda7d9b9ab92fa1224a28","tid":1980389,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset